So I just had this big long message written out, but i accidently cut it instead of pasted it. DAMN IT! lol.. and now I have to leave really soon like in 5 mins. What did I say.. oh yea.. This morning when MSN was still working he signed in before I left for work and I clicked on his name and BAM there it was.. oh HOT BABY!! shitttttt.. lol... and there IS a way to save those pictures!! lol... by taking a picture of the screen!! LOL.. Yes I'm a dork, but I had to do it for Karree.. I knew she could not go on living a normal life without having seen that. So i'm really excited to go get Zach. He was with my younger cousing Jonathan (who by the way is like right around 13 or 14.. if he stays serious with his hockey, he could be available for the Bantam draft soon!! :O could you imagine? I'll have to ask my aunt.. Wouldn't it be cool if he played in the DUB? (w) lol.. But he'd probably start out in the QHL.. do we even trade with the QHL or OHL? hmmm) but yea, so Zach had one of his old helmets and sticks and was just playing up and down the icy road.. aww!! how cute is that!! lol... oh look I should have left like 4 mins ago, but I think I pretty much re-created my original post. I HATE it when that happens.. gahh.. Well obviously I'm gonna have to read your message when I get home cause I'm leaving as soon as post my surprise (wink wink)

HAHA!!!!! yea you know you love it.. Now if we only could have Dan's matching one eh? ok ok ok, I'm leaving!! Talk to you when I get home, but I don't know when that will be!! probably around 1 am... if you have to go to bed that's fine, I'll talk to you tomorrow when (hopefully.. cross your fingers and your kristers) MSN will be back up.. LOVE YOU Mel

So to make a really lont story short, she accidently called her mom during the pizza show because of the time difference, she had no idea. Steph and Holly decided to ask Brenden if he'd talk to her on the phone. Apparantly he was like "Katie? My fan? oh yea!! Yea where's the phone!!" lol.. aww! And he said "hi Katie! Guess who!!" and she kept guessing wrong cause she had no idea and he was the last person she expected.  finally he said "No, it's me Brenden!" and I guess she was like "ohhh! hii!!" and they talked for like 5 minutes and finally he said "Hey Katie, I gotta go, but I hope you have a great week and I'll see you when you get home!" HOW freakin cute is THAT!!!! lol.. oh and I talked to Bri on AOL and she sent me the movie of the first time Derek ever winked at me.. OMG it is SO cute.
The smile he gave me after the wink.. it's enough to give me butterflies every time!! and she sent the movie of Robin coming into the locker room after he got ejected. you can see his mouth going, "FUCK!!!" lol... ok, I need to stop writing.. write back!

ps.. oh and I found out about that Perry Turnbull guy.. more. I'll tell you next message

Hey:)..well it sucks that msn isn't working, but at least we have our journal..I hope you're here...Well,I got an interview tomorrow!!!It's for a clothing store in coquitlam centre.. so i hope everything will go well...I'm nervousBut i'm excited that I ight get the job.it wouldn't be full time, but right now anything is better then nothing...I guess i'll leave it at that for ow...Write back...---Jawnell(Romy)

I stirred as the sound of the phone awoke me."Hello?" I said sleppily."Is Michael there?" an unfamilliar voice said. "wrong number." I replied calmly and hung up the phone. I looked at the clock on my bedside table, and as it came into focus I saw that it said 7:00am.I lay back in bed, groaning, because I knew that I wouldn't be able to fall back asleep. As i closed my eyes and stretched, I started to see visions of the dream I just had. I sat up quickly and covered my hand over my mouth.I thought immediatly of calling Jen and Jawnell to tell them about my dream, but I knew that neither one of them would appreciate an early morning wake up call. I knew that Karree, my room mate, wouldn't find my dream as interesting as they would, but Karree would definatley be up. As I enterred the kitchen, I smiled as I saw Karree eating her usual morning bowl of M&M's. "Karree, I kissed Dan!" I blurted out with a laugh. I sat down at the kitchen table beside her and continued to giggle."What?" she said with a confused expression."I kissed Dan Da Silva in my dream!"I clarrified. "Who's Dan Da Silva?" she asked, the puzzeld expression still on her face.I sighed, and smiled rememebring that Karree wasn't a big hockey fan like I was."From the Portland Winterhawks!#26!" I said leaving the table for a glass of water."Oh geez Melodie, you and your hockey."she said laughing."You're so obsessed that you're dreaming about them now too!" she enterred the kitchen and placed her almost finished bowl of M&M's on the counter."I'm not obsessed,"I said taking a long drink from my water glass, "I just had to tell someone about my dream because it was so random." I said defending myself."Ok! Even though I don't think the words hockey, you, and random go together, tell me what happened with you and Dan Da Silva in this dream" Karree asked."Not a lot actually happened," I started as I put my glass in the sink."I was at my old college getting ready for a lecture to begin; and the lecture hall was completley full except for one seat beside me.Dan came in, sat down beside me..." I stoppd and cleared my throat."And then he just kissed you?"Karree asked with a smile."Basically," I continued, "he sat down,looked at me with a little smile, leaned towards me, grabbed my face and then just kissed me."I sighed as I finished and Karree laughed."The wierd part is that it felt so real, it didn't feel like something I shouldn't be doing;it felt right."Well, I don't know what to tell you.I'll leave you with your thoughts, because if I don't leave for work right now i'll be late." She gave me a quick hug, grabbed her coat from the nearby closet, and left.I took a deep breath, looked around the kitchen, and groaned."I better clean this place up before i get ready for work or else i'll never get it done." I said out loud to myself.I worked quickly and soon the small appartment loked much better than before. Work that day started at 2:00 so not only was I able to take a long time getting ready without feeling rushed, but I was also able to email Jen and Jawnell about my dream.I sighed as I finished the email and tried to push the memory of the dream out of my mind."Don't get yourself caught up in this." I said sternally into the mirror.
                         ...............   
That night, after a long day at work, I received a 2-way phone call from Jen and Jawnell."So, did you have a chance to think about your dream with Dan today at work?"Jawnell asked with a smile to her voice."Work today was so busy, so no, and i'm trying not to. It was a really wierd dream, but I know that i shouldn't make too much out of this."I replied."I think it's natural for you to have dreamt about Dan, Melodie."Jen started." Think of how nice he's been to Zach lately."
"It makes perfect sence to me."Jawnell added.I smiled and looked up at the clock hanging on the wall."We'll have to talk more about this tomorrow at the game."I said yawning."But thank you. I'll pick you up at 5:30, Jawnell. Jen, we'll be at your place right after."I finished and hung up the phone.As I started getting ready for bed I thought about what Jen, Jawnell, and I had discussed. Dan had been really sweet these past few times with my six year old brother Zach.Zach had sudenly noticed how well Dan was playing and now liked him even more for his kindness."I suppose I just dreamed about Dan because I saw how good he was with Zach"I thought out loud.I shrugged away the thought and crawled under the covers on my unmade bed.
..............
When I pulled up to Jawnell's apartment the next evening the sun was already setting.My mother had called earlier on in the day and told me that Zach wanted to come to the game aswell,so I had picked him up on my way to Jawnell's.All ready he had dosed off in the back seat, I smiled as I stepped out of the car. From the street I could see Jawnell at her window on the 5th floor. She opened it and leaned out."Hi!" she shouted down to me."Wait right there ,and i'll be down in two minutes." I nodded,sat back down in the car, and closed to door quickly.I shivered and turned the heat up to the next setting.
